03:25.160 --> 03:28.795
I'm pretty kussed
from that last fight, man.

03:28.797 --> 03:31.130
Don't be a pussy.

03:31.132 --> 03:33.599
Radio didn't say
nothing about the coast guard.

03:33.601 --> 03:35.669
- [SIGHS]
- All we know, it's some...

03:35.671 --> 03:38.004
longliner out here, greedy.

03:38.006 --> 03:40.940
We... me and you...
we're going nowhere.

03:40.942 --> 03:43.610
We're gonna fish now, my friend.

03:43.612 --> 03:45.645
Let's fish.

03:45.647 --> 03:48.348
[♪♪♪]

03:48.350 --> 03:50.151
What was that?

03:58.827 --> 04:02.094
[BOTH YELL, GRUNT]

04:02.096 --> 04:06.832
- Hey, come, come. You all right?
- Fuck.

04:06.834 --> 04:08.835
[KWAME SPEAKS
IN FOREIGN LANGUAGE]

04:08.837 --> 04:10.803
That's a big one, <i>ek se.</i>

04:10.805 --> 04:12.605
And that's why
we're out here, baby.

04:12.607 --> 04:14.343
That's solid gold!

04:16.778 --> 04:19.848
[BOTH PANTING]

04:21.983 --> 04:23.319
Look...

04:24.519 --> 04:25.717
Are you seeing this?

04:25.719 --> 04:27.856
[♪♪♪]

04:34.163 --> 04:36.428
Have you seen
sharks swim like that?

04:36.430 --> 04:38.063
What are they doing?

04:38.065 --> 04:41.603
They're serving themselves
up on a platter. That's what.

04:45.639 --> 04:47.743
[SHARKS GROWL]

04:52.579 --> 04:54.015
[GASPING]

04:56.284 --> 04:57.286
[YELLING]

05:03.690 --> 05:05.293
[YELLING IN
FOREIGN LANGUAGE]

05:07.462 --> 05:08.661
Kwame!

05:08.663 --> 05:11.397
[SPUTTERING,
GASPING FOR BREATHE]

05:11.399 --> 05:13.433
[GASPS]
Fuck.

05:13.435 --> 05:15.402
[PAINED YELLS]

05:15.404 --> 05:16.671
Kwame!

05:30.685 --> 05:32.421
[SCREAMING]

05:44.865 --> 05:48.002
