You left me
down there to die!

01:22:45.815 --> 01:22:47.816
I should throw you
in there, you asshole!

01:22:47.818 --> 01:22:49.618
- TRENT: Hey, hey, hey!
- Get off of me!

01:22:49.620 --> 01:22:51.889
It's okay, there'll
be time for that later.

