Aaron!

01:25:28.511 --> 01:25:30.046
TRENT:
Aaron!

01:25:33.017 --> 01:25:34.684
MISTY:
Oh, no.

01:25:47.096 --> 01:25:48.232
[GRUNTS]

01:25:52.102 --> 01:25:54.738
[MUFFLED SCREAMS]

01:25:58.041 --> 01:26:00.040
[LAUGHS]

01:26:00.042 --> 01:26:03.011
I told you
I was Bella's master!

01:26:03.013 --> 01:26:05.181
[SCREAMING]

01:26:15.358 --> 01:26:17.495
[SHARK ROARS]

01:26:29.706 --> 01:26:31.772
[♪♪♪]

01:26:31.774 --> 01:26:33.844
[ALL PANTING]

01:26:36.313 --> 01:26:37.645
[ENGINE STALLING]

01:26:37.647 --> 01:26:39.213
Where's Bella?

01:26:39.215 --> 01:26:41.415
I don't see her.
I don't see her!

01:26:41.417 --> 01:26:44.485
Where...
