- pushed him in.
- Don't do that!

01:26:47.122 --> 01:26:49.490
- What?
- You were trying to save him.

01:26:49.492 --> 01:26:52.393
Oh, hey, she's back.

01:26:52.395 --> 01:26:53.927
She's back!

01:26:53.929 --> 01:26:56.633
